"Data Capture for DHIS 2" android application is a mobile client for DHIS 2 server instances. <br/>
In general, client is an interface for some of the core DHIS 2 functionality.<br/>
Application automatically downloads forms from DHIS 2 server and stores them on device.<br/>
Client supports an offline workflow, where app and its data entry can work even outside network coverage, and the data is submitted when there is network coverage available again.<br/><br/>
Developed by University of Oslo(UiO) (http://www.uio.no).<br/><br/>